{"tid":86192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"1月19日之聽日出gpa:用2分鐘睇晒各地新聞","createTime":"2017-01-19T01:13:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-20T01:03:41.000Z","uid":68591,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"be143ea8414456d05fc105f59f44a291bf5a322b","tid":86192,"uid":68591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T01:13:34.000Z","msg":"早晨! <br />\n<br />\n小弟想就尋日一則香港新聞道歉:<br />\n<br />\n有「上海仔」稱號的中年漢於元朗先遭車撞，後被刀手斬傷，兇徒事後逃去，而警方正追緝涉案兇徒。<br />\n<br />\n尋日可能有巴打絲打混淆左呢個上海仔係平時我地熟悉個個上海仔郭永鴻,但事實上佢係元朗一個同樣有上海仔稱號既人,我做得唔好,並且可能誤導左咁多位,小弟係到要講聲:好對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係知錯認錯改錯既人,下次會多加注意,希望咁多位原諒我今次既過失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外,尋日有巴打提議我係link後面加個個媒體既名,今日小弟就試下咁做,各位有咩意見請繼續提出<br />\n<br />\n長氣說話講完,夠鐘沖涼返學走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n每條新聞下面既link係新聞既sources,大家想進1步了解既可以入去條link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n港聞:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 梁振英發表任內最後一份《施政報告》，當中包括灣仔運動場改建為會展康體設施、建議郊野公園邊陲建公屋及逐步取消強積金與遣散費長期服務金對沖等。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2iT54H5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2iT54H5&d=TqJSYLXMWS6ujcf1pnLk0HvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=b92f01a1\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2iT54H5</a> (明報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2k1CjWq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2k1CjWq&d=TqJSYLXMWS6ujcf1pnLk0HvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=fe4b356a\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2k1CjWq</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2jAH3Wh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2jAH3Wh&d=TqJSYLXMWS6ujcf1pnLk0HvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=5369c3e6\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2jAH3Wh</a> (星島日報)<br />\n<a h